body_html:
I had the same problem. I had installed python with homebrew and thus had two copies
of numpy. I just renamed the old version, could erase it also:

$ sudo mv /System/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/2.7/Extras/lib/python/numpy/ /System/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/2.7/Extras/lib/python/numpy_bk
